  <div class="section">
    <h2>2. Text Formatting</h2>
    <p><b>Bold:</b> I really want to go to Paris.</p>
    <p><i>Italic:</i> I hope Italy has delicious food I've been wanting to try.</p>
    <p><u>Underlined:</u> London has great places to visit.</p>
    <p><strong>Strong:</strong> I must go to Californa someday!</p>
    <p><em>Emphasized:</em> The beaches in Puerto Rico look beautiful.</p>
  </div>

